{\tc\tcl3 \v \'C9tape 4 : CAN_setup_DF()}
Configure le header de transmission CAN (ID, type de frame, etc.).\par
{
\par
\pard\plain \s40\li0\widctlpar\adjustright \shading1000\cbpat8 \f2\fs16\cgrid {\cf18 void} CAN_setup_DF(int32_t std_id) \{\par
    std_id &= 0x7FFU;                {\cf20 // Masque pour ID standard 11 bits}\par
    TxHeader.IDE = CAN_ID_STD;       {\cf20 // Utiliser ID standard (non \'E9tendu)}\par
    TxHeader.StdId = std_id;         {\cf20 // Assigner l'ID CAN}\par
    TxHeader.RTR = CAN_RTR_DATA;     {\cf20 // Mode donn\'E9es (non RTR)}\par
    TxHeader.DLC = 8;                {\cf20 // Longueur = 8 octets}\par
\}\par
}
